    "Body": "Remote Woman Remote jobs at trusted companies Close Search for: Search Remote Jobs Marketing Design Developer Product Sales Support Success Stories Community Podcast Post Jobs Menu People Business Partner Full Time Anywhere Posted 1 week ago Hashicorp Overview About HashiCorp HashiCorp is a fast-growing startup that solves development, operations, and security challenges in infrastructure so organizations can focus on business-critical tasks. We build tools to ease these decisions by presenting solutions that span the gaps. Our tools manage both physical machines and virtual machines, Windows, and Linux, SaaS and IaaS, etc. About the Role We are looking for a People Business Partner to help support our growing company. This role will provide support to line managers across HashiCorp. The ideal candidate has experience in fast-paced, dynamic environments and can help scale/manage our rapid growth. We are seeking someone who can thrive in ambiguous situations and work collaboratively with all of our HashiCorp team members across the globe. They\u2019ll have a deep appreciation for what we do and a passion for how we do it. Success will be largely based on ability to build productive and positive relationships \u2013 but also on the desire to create replicable processes that can allow these relationships to thrive based on higher-order work. In this role, you can expect to: Manages and resolves employee relations issues. Escalates to more senior PBPs and/or Legal when needed. Partner and coach managers and individuals to ensure they and their teams are growing and meeting their individual and team objectives. Works closely with management and team members to improve work relationships, build morale, and increase productivity and retention. Analyzes trends and metrics in partnership with the larger People Team to develop solutions, programs, and opportunities for learning Partner with managers on people-related matters and decisions including organizational design, planning and compensation. Nurture our strong culture, providing role modeling of our principles and Tao. Drive equality, diversity, and inclusion throughout all of our people team programs and initiatives. You may be a good fit for our team if you have: 3+ years of People experience in recruiting, employee relations, people operations, compensation/benefits, and/or organizational development Discretion and sound judgment while working with sensitive and confidential materials Demonstrated past success supporting teams, preferably a rapidly growing tech organization Experience managing employee relations issues that includes participation in investigations, handling employee disciplinary issues, and performance management meetings Strong desire to help others and intellectual curiosity about people and organizational issues Analytically driven skills; experience working with people metrics to guide decisions Passion for results; able to deliver full-cycle projects (start to finish) and results in a timely manner. A team player who acts with a sense of urgency and adapts to a fast-paced and ever-changing environment Effective communication, and interpersonal skills; great listener Solid problem-solving capabilities and judgment; ability to make sound decisions independently Exceptional communication skills, specifically the ability to break down complex concepts into simple and clear language that anyone can understand Knowledge of equality, diversity, and inclusion approaches and history working on EDI initiatives HashiCorp embraces diversity and equal opportunity. We are committed to building a team that represents a variety of backgrounds, perspectives, and skills. We believe the more inclusive we are, the better our company will be. #LI-MM1 Apply for job Apply for job If this job interests you but you aren\u2019t certain if you meet all of theÂ requirements, apply anyway! More Jobs Website Twitter Or view all jobs: Developer jobs Marketing jobs Product j